config.value.tooltip.umu_backpack.freely: When ON or in creative mode, a backpack can be removed at any time. When OFF, in survival mode, a backpack cannot be removed if it contains items or is carrying an animal.
config.value.tooltip.umu_backpack.cram_e: Determines how often Cram enchantment is applied in enchantment table. Because the enchantment system goes through a complex algorithm, this does not guarantee a constant probability.
config.value.tooltip.umu_backpack.load_e: Determines how often Load enchantment is applied in enchantment table. Because the enchantment system goes through a complex algorithm, this does not guarantee a constant probability.
config.value.tooltip.umu_backpack.back_p: Determines how often Back Protection enchantment is applied in enchantment table. Because the enchantment system goes through a complex algorithm, this does not guarantee a constant probability.
modmenu.descriptionTranslation.umu_confi: A simple backpack mod. Small animals can also be carried in backpacks.
